title: How did the rookie QBs fare preseason week 1?
itunes:title: How did the rookie QBs fare preseason week 1?
description:
With preseason week 1 in the books, DJ and Bucky chat about Bears rookie linebacker’s, Roquan Smith, contract signing (1:10), rookie QBs first NFL games (5:48), Browns WR Antonio Callaway’s “punishment” (13:45), the guys also discuss if joint practices are worth the hassle following the Redskins & Jets training camp skirmish (17:00), Top-5 wideout preview ahead of 2018 (20:00), and MTS’s newest segment, Bucky’s Battle (25:00)!
